We found seasonal variation in the composition of the femoral gland secretions between G. g. eisentrauti and G. g. galloti populations (two-way PERMANOVA; population: pseudo F1,19 = 73.38, P < 0.001; season: pseudo F1,19 = 9.73, P < 0.01; interaction population × season: pseudo F1,19 = 1.99, P = 0.13). The CAP analyses classified 100% of individuals within the correct subspecies (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
